>>>> str(output)
>>> 'data.frame':   2 obs. of  1 variable:
>>>  $ para2: Factor w/ 2 levels "1","2H_map.txt": 1 2
>>>> str(input)
>>> 'data.frame':   2 obs. of  1 variable:
>>>  $ para1: Factor w/ 2 levels "1","2H.txt": 1 2
